octeon_droq_info_t Struct Reference

#include <octeon_droq.h>

Detailed Description

Information about packet DMA'ed by Octeon.

The format of the information available at Info Pointer after Octeon has posted a packet. Not all descriptors have valid information. Only the Info field of the first descriptor for a packet has information about the packet.
